did.head: Collection Summary

repository.label: Repository:
repository.corpname: Archives and Special Collections Library, Vassar College Libraries

did.abstract: Clippings, biographical information forms, news releases, memoranda, pamphlets, correspondence, photographs, book jackets, and articles. pertaining to the lives and careers of faculty, staff, administrators, trustees, and presidents of the college, as well as alumnae/i and other individuals with a siginificant relation to the development of the college.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content Note
scopecontent.p: Clippings, biographical information forms, news releases, memoranda, pamphlets, correspondence, photographs, book jackets, articles, and other items pertaining to the lives and careers of faculty, staff, administrators, trustees, and presidents, as well as alumnae/i and other individuals with a siginificant relation to the development of the college.

accessrestrict.head: Access
accessrestrict.p: This collection is open for research according to the regulations of the Vassar College Archives and Special Collections Library without any additional restrictions.

userestrict.head: Restrictions on Use
userestrict.p: Permission to quote (publish) from unpublished or previously published material must be obtained as described in the regulations of the Vassar College Archives and Special Collections Library.

p.extref: There is a card file on early faculty and staff that may contain additional biographical information. For additional information, please contact the Archives and Special Collections Library staff.

odd.head: Encoding Information
odd.p: Encoded by Elizabeth Clarke, May 2007. Last updated by Emma Gronbeck, February 2024.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: The bulk of the collection consists of transfers from the Office of Communications. Additional material has been added by various departments of the Library from multiple sources over several decades.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Vassar College Biographical Files, Archives and Special Collections Library, Vassar College Libraries.
